Decides if you can evade an attack or not.
This event only describes, if the player has enough TP to evade a certain attack skill.
Checks if actor has the required 10 TP.
If Yes: Chance to evade attack based of random number generator
If the random number = 1: 1/4 = 25% -> actor evades attack.
Else: 75% -> can not evade attack -> start action.
Checks if actor has the required 30 TP.
If Yes: Chance to evade attack based of random number generator
If the random number != 1: 2/3 = 66% -> actor evades attack.
Else: 33% -> can not evade attack -> start action.
Checks if actor has the required 50 TP.
If Yes: Chance to evade attack based of random number generator
If the random number != 1: 1/10 = 90% -> actor evades attack.
Else: 10% -> can not evade attack -> start action.
